## Summary

The past-session View button in /sections/[section_id]/page.tsx checks section.role === 'instructor' to decide routing, but section.role is set to the raw user.role string. For namespace-admins and system-admins, this check fails and they get routed to /student?session_id=... instead of /instructor/session/{id}.

## Files to modify

- frontend/src/app/(app)/sections/[section_id]/page.tsx

## Implementation steps

1. On line 278, replace the condition section.role === 'instructor' with the isInstructor boolean (which already checks for instructor, namespace-admin, and system-admin on line 106).

## Example

Before (line 277-280):
  onClick={() => router.push(
    section.role === 'instructor'
      ? /instructor/session/{session.id}
      : /student?session_id={session.id}
  )}

After:
  onClick={() => router.push(
    isInstructor
      ? /instructor/session/{session.id}
      : /student?session_id={session.id}
  )}

